  <brief_title>MSC Therapy in Liver Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>THIRD-PARTY BONE MARROW-DERIVED MESENCHYMAL STROMAL CELLS TO INDUCE TOLERANCE IN LIVER TRANSPLANT RECIPIENTS</official_title>
